Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "Monospace"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 12

# Launch pi with the extension loaded (cwd is the repo root)
Type "pi -e ." Enter
Sleep 3s

# Ask something that streams thinking so the sliding box is visible
Type "Explain how Pi's thinking-window box slides as tokens stream, in one paragraph." Enter
Sleep 12s
